      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "TO      : D. M. LADD",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "DATE: 9/16/47",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "FROM    : [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Special Agent [REDACTED] of the Liaison Section has dis-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "cussed with Lieutenant Colonel George [REDACTED] of the Intelligence",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Division of the Air Forces the possibility that the flying discs or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "saucers are in fact a project of the Army Air Forces. It should be noted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "that Colonel [REDACTED] agreed with this possibility. At that time Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "pointed out to Colonel [REDACTED] the possible embarrassing position of the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Intelligence Division of the Air Forces if it was subsequently ascertained",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "that this was the truth, especially since they had requested the assistance",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "of the Bureau in the captioned matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Colonel [REDACTED] advised Mr. [REDACTED] that he would institute a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "further search, and he has now advised that a letter was addressed by Major",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "General McDonald, Director of the Intelligence Division of the Air Forces, to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "the Research and Development Section of the Air Forces.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "There is attached hereto a letter addressed to the Director, dated",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "September 5, 1947, from Brigadier General George F. Schulgen, which states that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "a complete survey of research activities discloses that the Army Air Forces",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "have no project with characteristics similar to those which have been associated",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "with the flying discs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "RECOMMENDATION:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "It is recommended that this memorandum be forwarded to the Internal",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Security Section for their information.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
